I tell you this evening, there's none like Him.

457
00:33:05,659 --> 00:33:06,779
There's none like Him.

458
00:33:09,099 --> 00:33:14,099
The teachings of false religions and cults around the world,

459
00:33:15,259 --> 00:33:19,739
their desire of being able to put forth

460
00:33:19,739 --> 00:33:22,059
some understanding of who God is,

461
00:33:23,899 --> 00:33:28,019
it's all vague.

462
00:33:28,019 --> 00:33:30,219
I asked a man recently,

463
00:33:30,219 --> 00:33:34,219
how can you know if God is pleased with you?

464
00:33:35,659 --> 00:33:36,659
I have no idea.

465
00:33:38,099 --> 00:33:39,139
I have no idea.

466
00:33:40,139 --> 00:33:42,499
Well, we know in the Scriptures,

467
00:33:42,499 --> 00:33:43,739
we can go to the Word of God

468
00:33:43,739 --> 00:33:46,739
and we can find that these things please God.

469
00:33:46,739 --> 00:33:48,619
These things displease God.

470
00:33:48,619 --> 00:33:51,139
He revealed it to us.

471
00:33:51,179 --> 00:33:56,059
He communicated with us so that we could know Him,

472
00:33:56,059 --> 00:33:58,779
so that we could be accepted by Him,

473
00:33:58,779 --> 00:34:01,179
not in our own power and our own doing,

474
00:34:01,179 --> 00:34:03,779
but because of the fact that He died for us.

475
00:34:03,779 --> 00:34:06,299
And we have this great truth this evening.

476
00:34:06,299 --> 00:34:09,699
And the reality is that we're living in a time

477
00:34:09,699 --> 00:34:12,219
in which there's much confusion about who God is.

478
00:34:15,419 --> 00:34:16,539
Much confusion.

479
00:34:17,499 --> 00:34:19,179
God's never changed.

480
00:34:19,179 --> 00:34:20,899
Aren't you thankful for that?

481
00:34:21,659 --> 00:34:22,579
We spoke about the fact that He's omnipotent

482
00:34:22,579 --> 00:34:24,179
and He's omniscient.

483
00:34:24,179 --> 00:34:25,499
We understand that He's immutable.

484
00:34:25,499 --> 00:34:26,619
The fact that He doesn't change.

485
00:34:26,619 --> 00:34:28,019
He said, I change not.

486
00:34:29,379 --> 00:34:31,739
He's the same yesterday and today and forever.

487
00:34:34,859 --> 00:34:37,019
The reality this evening

488
00:34:37,019 --> 00:34:41,539
is that our God has made Himself known to us.

489
00:34:41,539 --> 00:34:42,739
What's in this book?

490
00:34:44,419 --> 00:34:47,059
We can accept who He is,

491
00:34:47,059 --> 00:34:49,019
or we can reject who He is,

492
00:34:49,979 --> 00:34:53,339
but we cannot redefine who He is.

493
00:34:53,339 --> 00:34:56,179
In seeking to do so,

494
00:34:56,179 --> 00:34:59,539
we simply are rejecting who He is,

495
00:34:59,539 --> 00:35:01,339
because we cannot redefine God.

496
00:35:02,339 --> 00:35:06,099
God has revealed Himself to mankind.

497
00:35:06,099 --> 00:35:09,099
And this evening, as we begin the start of this journey

498
00:35:09,099 --> 00:35:12,099
in this three-part study of theology,

499
00:35:12,099 --> 00:35:15,339
I hope tonight that you would rejoice

500
00:35:15,339 --> 00:35:18,939
in the fact that God, in His grace and His mercy,

501
00:35:19,779 --> 00:35:22,699
has allowed you to know the truth of who He is.

502
00:35:24,299 --> 00:35:26,099
But then that we would acknowledge

503
00:35:26,099 --> 00:35:28,659
that in the midst of such confusion,

504
00:35:31,619 --> 00:35:34,019
in really the days in which we're living

505
00:35:34,019 --> 00:35:37,139
in all-out attack on who God is,

506
00:35:38,419 --> 00:35:42,019
that we'd understand the opportunity that God has given us

507
00:35:42,019 --> 00:35:46,179
to declare Him to a lost and dying world.

508
00:35:47,139 --> 00:35:48,579
Because there are people that just flat out

509
00:35:49,219 --> 00:35:51,019
don't know who God is.

510
00:35:51,019 --> 00:35:54,659
They have their own little image of who they think God is.

511
00:35:55,899 --> 00:35:58,659
But we don't have to rely on some other source,

512
00:35:58,659 --> 00:36:01,659
we just go to His source.

513
00:36:02,939 --> 00:36:04,859
And this evening, as we would rejoice

514
00:36:04,859 --> 00:36:07,179
in what God has given us,

515
00:36:07,179 --> 00:36:10,219
I pray that God would help us to understand

516
00:36:10,219 --> 00:36:15,219
the responsibility to share that truth.

517
00:36:15,779 --> 00:36:18,539
Paul says, Him declare I unto thee.

518
00:36:18,539 --> 00:36:22,099
He says, how shall they hear without a preacher?

519
00:36:24,219 --> 00:36:25,299
We live in a society, we say,

520
00:36:25,299 --> 00:36:27,059
how can people think that way?

521
00:36:28,259 --> 00:36:30,339
You listen to the things that people say,

522
00:36:30,339 --> 00:36:32,499
and you say, how can they think that way?

523
00:36:32,499 --> 00:36:33,859
They don't know who God is.

524
00:36:34,899 --> 00:36:36,859
They don't know the truth of this book.

525
00:36:38,019 --> 00:36:39,059
Who's gonna tell them?

526
00:36:40,459 --> 00:36:44,299
Not the schoolteachers, right?

527
00:36:45,219 --> 00:36:48,259
Not Hollywood, not the politicians.

528
00:36:49,339 --> 00:36:51,339
No, not the media.

529
00:36:52,499 --> 00:36:53,939
Who's gonna tell them?

530
00:36:53,939 --> 00:36:56,779
Somebody that knows the truth, you and I.

531
00:36:56,779 --> 00:36:58,419
Stand up and give the truth.

532
00:36:58,419 --> 00:36:59,259
Let's pray.

533
00:36:59,259 --> 00:37:00,179
Father, we love you.

534
00:37:00,179 --> 00:37:01,819
Thank you for loving us.

535
00:37:01,819 --> 00:37:05,139
Thank you for revealing yourself to us through your word.

536
00:37:08,939 --> 00:37:12,579
We acknowledge this evening that we've been blessed.

537
00:37:14,579 --> 00:37:19,579
To know the truth of your word

538
00:37:20,659 --> 00:37:22,739
as you revealed yourself to us.

539
00:37:26,339 --> 00:37:31,339
I pray that as we, over the next couple of weeks,

540
00:37:31,859 --> 00:37:34,219
study the subject matter of theology,

541
00:37:34,219 --> 00:37:36,459
that our hearts would just rejoice.

542
00:37:37,939 --> 00:37:39,579
The very same time, I pray, God,

543
00:37:39,579 --> 00:37:43,739
that you'd help us to recognize the importance

544
00:37:44,579 --> 00:37:47,579
of proclaiming this truth to a lost and dying world.

545
00:37:48,739 --> 00:37:51,859
Understanding that there are so many in our society

546
00:37:54,419 --> 00:37:55,539
that do not know you.

547
00:38:00,579 --> 00:38:03,019
I pray, God, that you would help us.

548
00:38:03,019 --> 00:38:04,059
Bless our time of prayer.

549
00:38:04,059 --> 00:38:06,939
We thank you for the privilege of prayer.

550
00:38:06,939 --> 00:38:08,939
We pray that you would be honored and glorified

551
00:38:08,939 --> 00:38:10,099
through the remainder of our service.

552
00:38:10,099 --> 00:38:13,299
For it's in Christ's name we pray, amen.

553
00:38:13,299 --> 00:38:15,219
I did send out the prayer bulletin via email

554
00:38:15,219 --> 00:38:16,899
